flowRoot.flowPara: Change Settings... and Add Another Profile... both launch the setup assistant.
Settings button opens the settings dialog.
When use recommended settings is selected, the mobile broadband, PPP and IPv4 sections are insensitive - they can be viewed but not edited.
Change Profile Details... launches the setup assistant.
System modal dialog pops up when a locked SIM is inserted.
If the SIM isn't unlocked straight away, it is possible to unlock it from the settings panel.
